{
  "stem": "8947.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And my father, I think, wanted to ignore that, so that I'm not too unhappy to find it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "We went to the temple.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Like Yom Kippur, the Day of Atonement, we were the whole day in the temple.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "We were fasting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And we had the feast in the evening.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And we went to the Orthodox temple for-- for services.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And then New Year's-- Passover, my mother was working.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "My god, every single crumb had to be taking care of, so that you don't have anything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "The new dishes were taken in for Passover dishes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "Everything was sterilized.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And then we had the Passover matzoh and all the Passover flour, I mean, Passover dishes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "I-- you know, I have a news clipping here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "I will show you maybe later on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "It's a picture of me and my mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And the interviewer came at Passover.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And she was preparing the matzoh balls, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "Well, and I-- I feel that I was fortunate to grow up, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And-- also Sukkot, we-- we had a-- we had a whole ritual.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "You know, usually my grandfather, my grandmother had to attend there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And these were nice memories that kept me alive the camps.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "Believe me, it did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It's-- you know, forgive me that I get the emotional.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "But that's natural, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "Not only that they kept me alive in the camps, but if I want to think back, you know, of some wonderful things in my life, they still give me enjoyment.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "Although I'm getting older now, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "But-- but I grew up-- once you grew up with that, it stays with you for you a lifetime.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "I hope I didn't talk too much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "But the subject was very-- very close to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
